        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Items</head>
                <p xml:id="del-2023-02-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_033-5a.6" xml:lang="en" modified="2023-02-02T00:41:36.788+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3j0080-en-b4d80944">and not being a virtuou, then is a flatter.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_033-5a.8" xml:lang="en" modified="2023-02-02T00:41:55.38+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3j0080-en-b4d80944">have no high telligence, and cannot come up to the virtuous.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_033-5a.2" xml:lang="en" modified="2023-02-02T00:43:04.477+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3j0080-en-b4d80944">Somebody ask:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T02:55:40.244+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR1h0001">extrapolates from those he loves to those he does not love CH</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-79a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2023-02-02T03:09:33.136+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When he is delighted, he does not increase easiness, (or: When one is happy, things do not become easier)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-79a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2023-02-02T03:10:21.244+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">when he feels anger, he does not add (&gt;impose) difficulties. (or: when one is angry, things do not become more difficult)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-79a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T03:10:33.936+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When he is in a good mood he does not become easier to deal with,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-79a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T03:11:08.148+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and when is in angry spirits he does</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-79a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#dsehnal" modified="2023-02-02T03:11:37.944+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and speaks up in accordance with the right principles.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:00:55.313+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and yet that is what Shen Tudi did</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:04:25.032+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and yet that is what Shen Tudi did:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:05:56.942+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Robber</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:17:55.001+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">but the gentlemen have never cared for him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:19:42.624+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Robber Zhi was wickedly greedy</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:22:53.133+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">alongside with Shun and Yu his story was transmitted incessantly</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:27:09.396+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and the gentleman refuse to honour him for it;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:30:15.113+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">but the gentleman has never cared for him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-73a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-02T06:33:10.008+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and the gentleman refuses to commend him for it;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:10:57.024+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-fr-46f1913b">ce qui fait 10 fin (d'intérêt) pour un jour,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:11:05.964+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-fr-46f1913b">Ici, on peut en outre simplifier par les 30 jours que comporte un mois l'intérêt de30 sapèques,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:16:00.04+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">-multiply</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:17:14.136+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">-multiply the given amount of cash presumed for one day with it and take it as</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:17:31.135+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">-multiply the given amount of cash presumed for one day with it and take it as the dividend</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:20:17.295+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">As for lü,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:22:55.246+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">we should equalize is to the unit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:23:16.376+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">we should make them equal to the unit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:23:39.892+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">thy should be made them equal to the unit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s8-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:29:18.464+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">Therefore, by the 30 days, one can either multiply the original</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s8-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:35:17.682+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In any case, </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:35:42.772+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">-multiply the given amount of cash presumed for one day with it and take [the result] as the dividend.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:35:48.441+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">*multiply the given amount of cash presumed for one day with it and take [the result] as the dividend.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s8-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:48:16.86+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In any case, it is a way to make them equal.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T08:51:39.536+09:00" resp-del="#andrea.breard" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">we should make them equal to the unit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T17:14:41.528+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">Take 1000 cash as dividend.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T17:36:08.045+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">one should make them equal to the unit.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s8-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T17:37:51.988+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In either case, it is a way to make them equal.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-02T17:38:35.452+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">As for the lü,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-02T17:47:39.641+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">As for the [numbers] that constitute the lü,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s7-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-02T17:48:11.256+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">one should make them correspond to 'one' (day).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s8-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-02T17:48:29.568+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In either case, it is a way to make them (the lüs) equal.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s8-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-02T17:49:46.872+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In either case, it is a way to make them (the lü) equal.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s6-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-02T17:58:27.484+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">As an alternative to this, one could simplify (divide) the interest of 30 cash with the 30 days in a month;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:18:57.08+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">dico tamen, quod quisquis probe intellexerit arcanas illas ac sublimes ritus hujus </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:19:21.642+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">dico tamen, quod quisquis probe intellexerit arcanas illas ac sublimes ritus hujus </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:20:07.327+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">ac si posita videret omnia hic, in palma, inquam</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:21:35.739+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">is habiturus sit omnia tam perspecta, tamque in promptu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:37:29.147+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:48:57.169+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">hoc, inquam, proverbium quid obsecro significant? Praefectus ille plurimum valebat gratia </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:49:04.51+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">hoc, inquam, proverbium quid obsecro significant? Praefectus ille plurimum valebat gratia </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T22:56:14.194+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">non habet aliud Numen superius a quo peccati veniam deprecetur.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-15a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2023-02-05T23:03:54.263+09:00" resp-del="#twharbsmeier" src-id="KR1h0004-la-12f4bc6a">Haec, quae nunc rerum potitur, familia Cheu; in ortu suo statim conjecit oculos in duas familias Hia </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0007a-s2-seg6a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:04:22.448+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">Afterwards,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s1-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:07:16.656+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">By multiplying the number of bù for width and length with each other, one obtains (results in???) the product in bù (the area in square bù). </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s1-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:07:29.981+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">By multiplying the number of bù for breadth and length with each other, one obtains (results in???) the product in bù (the area in square bù). </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s3-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:07:53.108+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">As for [the result of] the multiplication of width and length, it is called "mi" (area/a shape?).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s4-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:08:20.33+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In the book, it says that by multiplying the width and length with each other leads to the obtainment of the area in bù,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s4-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:08:31.961+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">and in the commentary, it says that [when] multiplying width and length with each other, you are calling [the result] a shape. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s6-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:09:12.388+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">If one, by logic (using logic), pushes (pursues?) this further</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s6-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:09:44.004+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">what would be indubitably adequate is not this.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s17-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-06T16:11:34.429+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-fr-46f1913b"> 100 MU FONT 1 QING.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s20-seg6a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:12:17.648+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">then every row's width is one bù and [their] length is 16 bù.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s21-seg3a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:12:25.28+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">and then each row's width/breadth would be one bù and (its) length would be 15 bù.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s24-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:12:47.919+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">that by multiplying width/breadth with length, one obtains the product in bù.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s25-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:13:16.151+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">is the model for mǔ (is what mǔ imitates/models itself after = the same as mǔ?);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a05.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-06T16:14:23.655+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Yang Jie</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0038a-s25-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:14:24.643+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">is the model for qǐng.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0049a-s1-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:26:23.676+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">Now assume there was a field that was one lǐ wide</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0052a-s1-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:26:42.083+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">Moreover, presume there was a field that was 2 lǐ in width</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0054a-s1-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:26:53.77+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">When you multiply the number of lǐ of the width and length with each other, you get the product in lǐ (i. e. the measurements of the surface in lǐ). </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0054a-s3-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:27:05.768+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">In this exercise, multiplying the number of lǐ of [both] width/breadth and length leads to obtaining the product in lǐ.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0054a-s4-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-02-06T16:27:35.745+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-fr-46f1913b">c'est pourquoi en multiplier ceci (le produit) donne comme résultat la quantité (shu) de mu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0056a-s1-seg2a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:27:53.14+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">[and] ask [yourself]: If you reduced this, what would [you] get?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0060a-s1-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:28:54.546+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">they cannot be used up in their entirety (brought down to 0? Discuss!)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0060a-s1-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:30:56.006+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">they are not complete numbers (they do not have a value that is </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0060a-s1-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:31:18.895+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">they are not (cannot be) whole numbers</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0060a-s1-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:31:29.199+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">they cannot be whole numbers</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0060a-s2-seg4a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:32:35.692+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">(however) if you put this in a reduced way</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3f0032_tls_001-p0623a-s1-seg1a" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2023-02-06T16:58:23.408+09:00" resp-del="#Valerie.Kiel" src-id="KR3f0032-en-bcc232c0">Procedure:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s19" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T16:46:55.039+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">At the beginning of the [Song] regime, Chan Master [Yan]shou, “Wisdom-</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s19" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T16:47:00.229+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">At the beginning of the [Song] regime, Chan Master [Yan]shou, “Wisdom-Enlightenment,”  of Yongming [Monastery] in Wuyue,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s19" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T16:47:53.419+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">ascended the highest vehicle</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s46" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T16:54:35.378+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">they will know that the moral precepts, meditation, and wisdom are the im-</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s59" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:08:11.813+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">There will be nothing to do, no place to</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s58" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:08:29.615+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">they will know that peaceful tranquility generated by spiritual illumination expands freely and harmoniously.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a0701.s59" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:08:31.485+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415a2801.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:13:46.634+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">a younger brother of the emperor, Wei Duan,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b07.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:20:18.794+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Preface</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b09.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:20:20.082+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Written by Prince [Qian] Chu of the Principality of Wuyue</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b09.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:20:41.536+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">three teachings within the boundaries of our territory.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b07.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:20:59.113+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">There are</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b09.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:21:11.01+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b1001.s27" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:28:56.881+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">was compiled by Chan master　“Wisdom-Enlightenment” [Yongming Yanshou]. It consists of one hundred</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b26.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T17:34:43.309+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Collected by Yanshou, Chan Master “Wisdom-Enlightenment,” Chief Priest of</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s31" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T18:17:41.012+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">We create an [ultimate] destination, when [in reality] there is no such thing. When summarizing the circumstances living beings inhabit, they are divided into twenty-ﬁve abodes. 13</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s34" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-07T18:19:18.667+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">In all cases, it is as a result of emotions, mental conceptions, and sense-faculties that differences in “dependent” and “direct” karmic rewards are encountered.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-2a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-07T21:37:49.972+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3j0010-fr-9c668d8f">on inventa des armes en dondant le métal [§§作為之 is grammatically misconstrued by the English "created for them" and the French does not better. The phrase remains puzzling.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s49" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:39:33.926+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">manifests the regulated patterns of the triple realm.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s58" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:43:58.363+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">perceiving them as phenomena other than ourselves.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s57" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:44:05.863+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">We create phantom, illusory appearances and sounds,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s56" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:44:19.809+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">we do not know how to return to the root [i.e., our original enlightened nature]. We conceive perverse, chaotic views that obscure [the truth] inherent in our own minds.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s57" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:44:32.279+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s58" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:44:34.216+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s73" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:49:33.188+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Some attained Buddhahood suddenly,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s72" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:50:19.328+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Some gradually assimilated the methods of practice through an infusion of training methods over a period of three aeons.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s73" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:50:44.019+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s74" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:51:54.527+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">through the perfect cultivation of a single thought,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s75" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T14:52:01.594+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Some attained Buddhahood suddenly,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s95" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:01:01.936+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Beginners who are confused about it refer to it as [the realm of ] birth and death. They, moreover, maintain roots of depravity and</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s115" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:06:58.117+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Put an end to illusory substances [of consciousness] and imaginary images will</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s119" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:08:58.526+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Use the sword of wisdom emanating from self-awakening to rip open the mind-pearl that has been tightly</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s121" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:09:53.794+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">to sever the web of views formed in connection with the illusory objects of the external realm.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s120" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:10:03.657+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Use the spear of insight emanating from a single-thought</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s119" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:10:22.337+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">Use the sword of wisdom emanating from self-awakening to rip open the mind-pearl that has been tightly concealed within.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s120" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:10:31.462+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s121" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:10:33.362+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s118" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:10:39.325+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059">When the Buddha-eye illuminates them, karmically produced images are empty. When the Dharma-body is revealed, the traces of illusory objects disappear.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s119" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:10:41.883+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0092_CBETA_000-0415b2801.s134" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2023-02-08T15:15:33.438+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0092-en-405f6059"> [The objectiﬁed realm of ] name and form will face the rays of the wisdom-sun, and will be released into the sea of universal truth.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-4a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-08T18:52:18.239+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3j0010-fr-9c668d8f">si l'on veut mener à bien les affaires [§§§§周於"be comprehensively helpful (to the task) remains untranslated in the English. §§§§苟 is again mistranslated.]</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
